name: Dell Inspiron 15 3501 Core i3
proshortdisc:
Dell Inspiron 15 3501 Core i3 10th Generation Laptop in Pakistan
Who wouldn't desire to have premium specs at a modest price? This Dell Inspiron 3501 offers you the latest specs at an affordable price. It has a 10th generation processor, a medium-size display with a lot of features, and everything you can expect on any latest laptop in Pakistan. Here is what it brings to you:
prodisc:
Processor
This latest Dell 3501 laptop in Pakistan comes with one of the best 10th Generation Core i3-1005G1 Dual Core Processor. Its 2 Cores - 4 Threads combination is powerful enough to handle a lot of applications. Moreover, this system has a DualCore processor, which optimizes the device exceptionally to provide some multitasking. Its speed starts at 1.2 GHz that can rise to 3.4 GHz with Intel's Turbo Boost Technology. Alongside this, you get 4 MB caching memory.
Ram & Storage
Entry-level laptops do not usually include heavy-duty ram and storage. Keeping that tradition, this Dell Inspiron 3000 Series comes with 04 GB DDR4 with a 2666MHz transfer rate. However, you can increase it anytime you wish to. On the other side, it offers 1 TeraByte Hard Disk Drive with an average 5400 RPM speed. You can add a solid-state drive with the HDD if you want!
Graphics
Moving into the next category, the Dell Inspiron 3501 10th Gen comes with mostly used Intel UHD Graphics. These graphics use a shared memory slot. It has Intel's graphics processor that offers an immersive visual experience. These visuals allow you to use all business and utility software without any hassle.
Display
This Dell Core i3 Laptop in Pakistan comes in a 15.6-inch Full High Definition Display with (1920 x 1080) or 1080P resolution. This size and resolution in an entry-level device are amazing to have. Apart from that, it has a WVA Display along with some other features like Anti-glare, Non-Touch, LED Backlight. All these specs are amazing to have with this price tag.
Other Specs
It comes in a Catchy Black finish. It weighs around 1.83 kg. It offers all the necessary connectivity options such as Bluetooth, WiFi, and LAN. Alongside this, it contains 2 USB 3.2 Gen 1 Type-A ports, 1 USB 2.0 Gen 1 Type-A port, 1 HDMI v1.4, 720p at 30 fps HD camera, single-array microphone, and DOS as the primary OS.
